  "chapter": {
    "bookTitle": "2 Timothy",
    "delineation": "Chapter",
    "number": 3,
    "summary": "Paul describes the apostasy and perilous times of the last days—The scriptures guide man to salvation.",
    "chapterAugmentations": [],
    "verses": [
      {
        "text": "This know also, that in the last days perilous times shall come.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Morm. 1:17 (13–17); 8:28 (26–33). TG Last Days.",
            "start": 28,
            "end": 37
          },
          {
            "footnote": "2 Tim. 4:3.",
            "start": 47,
            "end": 52
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [
          {
            "class": "iconPointer-OKie_ icon-eLakR icon-ieVZ1",
            "data-pointer-type": "media",
            "data-scroll-id": "p1",
            "title": "Associated Content"
          }
        ],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "For men shall be lovers of their own selves, covetous, boasters, proud, blasphemers, disobedient to parents, unthankful, unholy,",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Covet.",
            "start": 45,
            "end": 53
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Pride.",
            "start": 65,
            "end": 70
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Contention; Disobedience; Family, Children, Duties of.",
            "start": 85,
            "end": 96
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Ingratitude.",
            "start": 109,
            "end": 119
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Without natural affection, trucebreakers, false accusers, incontinent, fierce, despisers of those that are good,",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Rom. 1:26 (26–28).",
            "start": 8,
            "end": 15
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Sexual Immorality.",
            "start": 16,
            "end": 25
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Honesty.",
            "start": 27,
            "end": 40
          },
          {
            "footnote": "GR slanderers.",
            "start": 42,
            "end": 56
          },
          {
            "footnote": "GR without self-control.",
            "start": 58,
            "end": 69
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Traitors, heady, highminded, lovers of pleasures more than lovers of God;",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Rebellion.",
            "start": 0,
            "end": 8
          },
          {
            "footnote": "GR rash, reckless.",
            "start": 10,
            "end": 15
          },
          {
            "footnote": "GR puffed up, conceited.",
            "start": 17,
            "end": 27
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Pleasure.",
            "start": 39,
            "end": 48
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Having a form of godliness, but denying the power thereof: from such turn away.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Rom. 2:20; 2 Ne. 28:5; JS—H 1:19.",
            "start": 9,
            "end": 13
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church.",
            "start": 32,
            "end": 39
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "For of this sort are they which creep into houses, and lead captive silly women laden with sins, led away with divers lusts,",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Woman.",
            "start": 74,
            "end": 79
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Lust.",
            "start": 118,
            "end": 123
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Ever learning, and never able to come to the knowledge of the truth.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Learn.",
            "start": 5,
            "end": 13
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Ignorance; Knowledge.",
            "start": 45,
            "end": 54
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Truth.",
            "start": 62,
            "end": 67
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Now as Jannes and Jambres withstood Moses, so do these also resist the truth: men of corrupt minds, reprobate concerning the faith.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Opposition.",
            "start": 60,
            "end": 66
          },
          {
            "footnote": "Ps. 14:1; D&C 10:21 (20–23); 112:23 (23–24).",
            "start": 85,
            "end": 92
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "But they shall proceed no further: for their folly shall be manifest unto all men, as theirs also was.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "D&C 35:7; 45:49; 63:15.",
            "start": 45,
            "end": 50
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": [
          {
            "start": 78,
            "end": 82
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "But thou hast fully known my doctrine, manner of life, purpose, faith, longsuffering, charity, patience,",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "GR followed closely, conformed to.",
            "start": 14,
            "end": 25
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Persecutions, afflictions, which came unto me at Antioch, at Iconium, at Lystra; what persecutions I endured: but out of them all the Lord delivered me.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Acts 15:26.",
            "start": 86,
            "end": 98
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": [
          {
            "start": 121,
            "end": 125
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Yea, and all that will live godly in Christ Jesus shall suffer persecution.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "TG Godliness.",
            "start": 28,
            "end": 33
          },
          {
            "footnote": "Ps. 34:19. TG Suffering.",
            "start": 56,
            "end": 62
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Cruelty; Persecution.",
            "start": 63,
            "end": 74
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "But evil men and seducers shall wax worse and worse, deceiving, and being deceived.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "GR diviners, imposters, cheats.",
            "start": 17,
            "end": 25
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "But continue thou in the things which thou hast learned and hast been assured of, knowing of whom thou hast learned them;",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "D&C 66:12.",
            "start": 4,
            "end": 12
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": [
          {
            "start": 116,
            "end": 121
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "And that from a child thou hast known the holy scriptures, which are able to make thee wise unto salvation through faith which is in Christ Jesus.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "Deut. 4:9 (6–9).",
            "start": 16,
            "end": 21
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Scriptures, Study of.",
            "start": 47,
            "end": 57
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Understanding.",
            "start": 87,
            "end": 91
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Salvation.",
            "start": 97,
            "end": 106
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      },
      {
        "text": "All scripture is given by inspiration of God, and is profitable for doctrine, for reproof, for correction, for instruction in righteousness:",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "JST 2 Tim. 3:16 And all scripture given by inspiration of God, is profitable …",
            "start": 0,
            "end": 3
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Book of Mormon; Scriptures, Writing of; Scriptures to Come Forth.",
            "start": 4,
            "end": 13
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Inspiration.",
            "start": 26,
            "end": 37
          },
          {
            "footnote": "GR beneficial or useful for instruction.",
            "start": 53,
            "end": 63
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Scriptures, Value of.",
            "start": 68,
            "end": 76
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Chastening; Reproof.",
            "start": 82,
            "end": 89
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Education.",
            "start": 111,
            "end": 122
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Righteousness.",
            "start": 126,
            "end": 139
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": [
          {
            "start": 14,
            "end": 16
          },
          {
            "start": 50,
            "end": 52
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "That the man of God may be perfect, throughly furnished unto all good works.",
        "footnotes": [
          {
            "footnote": "GR suited, ready, complete. TG Perfection.",
            "start": 27,
            "end": 34
          },
          {
            "footnote": "TG Good Works.",
            "start": 65,
            "end": 75
          }
        ],
        "associatedContents": [],
        "italics": []
      }
    ]
  }
}